---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Marketing Services | OnlineMarketingCORE">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Our Marketing Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Comprehensive digital marketing solutions powered by 25+ years of experience and proprietary technology.
      </p>
      <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Placeholder for Services SVG -->
        <div class="bg-gray-200 h-64 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-gray-500">Integrated Services SVG Illustration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Overview Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Approach to Marketing Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          At OnlineMarketingCORE, we deliver data-driven marketing services designed to maximize ROI and drive measurable business growth. Our integrated approach ensures all marketing channels work together seamlessly, amplifying results across your entire digital presence.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Each service is delivered by specialized teams with deep expertise in their field, supported by our proprietary CORE platform that provides unparalleled insights and automation capabilities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Grid Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Our Service Categories</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <a href="./services/seo" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">SEO Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Search Engine Optimization</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Improve your organic visibility and drive sustainable traffic with our comprehensive SEO strategies.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./services/paid-search" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Paid Search Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Paid Search (SEA)</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Drive targeted traffic and generate leads through strategically managed paid search campaigns.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./services/content-marketing" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Content Marketing Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Content Marketing</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Engage your audience with valuable, relevant content that drives traffic and conversions.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./services/social-media" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Social Media Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Social Media Marketing</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Build your brand and engage with your audience across the most relevant social platforms.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./services/website-optimization" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Website Optimization Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Website Optimization</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Improve user experience and conversion rates through data-driven website enhancements.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./services/website-development" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Website Development Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Website Development</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Create high-performance, conversion-focused websites built with marketing in mind.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./services/ecommerce-marketing" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">E-Commerce Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">E-Commerce Marketing</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Specialized strategies to drive traffic, increase conversions, and maximize customer lifetime value.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./technology/marketing-automation" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Marketing Automation Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Marketing Automation</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Streamline and optimize your marketing processes with intelligent automation solutions.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="./technology/tracking-solutions" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Tracking Solutions Icon</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Tracking & Analytics</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Gain actionable insights with comprehensive tracking and advanced analytics solutions.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Methodology Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Service Methodology</h2>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/4 flex justify-center">
              <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-800 text-2xl font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-3/4">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Discovery & Analysis</h3>
              <p>We begin by understanding your business goals, market position, and current performance. Our team conducts thorough audits to identify opportunities and challenges that inform our strategy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/4 flex justify-center">
              <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-800 text-2xl font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-3/4">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Strategy Development</h3>
              <p>Based on our findings, we create a customized strategy that aligns with your business objectives. This includes channel selection, budget allocation, and defining key performance indicators.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/4 flex justify-center">
              <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-800 text-2xl font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-3/4">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Implementation</h3>
              <p>Our specialized teams execute the strategy with meticulous attention to detail, leveraging our proprietary technology to ensure efficiency and effectiveness across all channels.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/4 flex justify-center">
              <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-800 text-2xl font-bold">4</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-3/4">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Monitoring & Optimization</h3>
              <p>We continuously monitor performance against KPIs, making data-driven adjustments to optimize results. Regular reporting keeps you informed of progress and insights.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/4 flex justify-center">
              <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-800 text-2xl font-bold">5</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-3/4">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Evaluation & Scaling</h3>
              <p>We regularly evaluate overall strategy effectiveness, identifying opportunities to scale successful tactics and adjust underperforming elements to continuously improve ROI.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">What Our Clients Say</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-gray-200 w-12 h-12 rounded-full mr-4"></div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Sarah Johnson</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Marketing Director, Tech Innovations</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-4">"OnlineMarketingCORE transformed our digital marketing strategy. Their data-driven approach to SEO and paid search has resulted in a 45% increase in quality leads and a significant improvement in ROI."</p>
            <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
              <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-gray-200 w-12 h-12 rounded-full mr-4"></div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Michael Chen</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">CEO, E-Commerce Solutions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-4">"The team at OnlineMarketingCORE has been instrumental in scaling our e-commerce business. Their integrated approach across SEO, PPC, and social media has delivered consistent growth in revenue month over month."</p>
            <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
              <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a href="/success-stories/testimonials" class="text-blue-600 font-medium">View More Testimonials →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How do you determine which services are right for my business?</h3>
            <p>We conduct a thorough assessment of your business goals, target audience, and current marketing performance to recommend the optimal service mix. Our approach is never one-size-fits-all; we tailor services to your specific needs and objectives.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Do you offer bundled service packages?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we offer integrated service packages designed to maximize results through complementary channels. These bundles are customized based on your business goals and typically provide cost efficiencies compared to individual services.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How do you measure the success of your services?</h3>
            <p>We establish clear KPIs at the beginning of our engagement, aligned with your business objectives. Regular reporting tracks progress against these metrics, providing transparency and accountability throughout our partnership.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What makes your services different from other agencies?</h3>
            <p>Our differentiators include our proprietary CORE technology platform, 25+ years of experience, data-driven methodologies, and specialized teams with deep expertise in their respective fields. We focus on ROI and business outcomes rather than vanity metrics.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What is the typical timeline for seeing results?</h3>
            <p>Timelines vary by service. Paid search can generate immediate traffic, while SEO typically shows significant improvements within 3-6 months. We set realistic expectations during strategy development and provide regular updates on progress.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-blue-700 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to transform your marketing performance?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">Schedule a free consultation with our experts to discuss your goals and discover how we can help.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block py-3 px-8 bg-white text-blue-700 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">Book Your Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout> 
